metadata.description: This collection features an initial run of 485 AI-generated hot air balloons. Sometimes blimpish, sometimes steampunk, sometimes vivid, sometimes dreamy -- but always wild, magical, and inspiring. May these greetings lift up each recipient. Thanks for collecting! From all of us at NFTGreetings.xyz and GenerativeNFTs.io. :-)
metadata.name: NFTGreetings: AI Hot Air Balloons #1
